window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Master Italian with <i>Learn Italian - Word Power 101</i>. This audiobook is a completely new way to learn Italian vocabulary fast - and for free! Start speaking Italian in minutes with the powerful learning methods you will master in this book. </p><p>The vocabulary words you'll find in <i>Learn Italian - Word Power 101</i> were hand selected by our Italian language teachers as the top 101 most frequently used words in the Italian language. Hear the word to master the pronunciation. Then you'll see how the word is actually used in everyday speech with sample sentences and phrases. Learning Italian vocabulary has never been easier! </p><p>In this audiobook, you'll get: </p><li>101 of the most frequently used Italian vocabulary words phrases. </li><li>Audio with authentic native Italian pronunciation. </li><li>Useful and practical sample sentences and phrases. </li><p>Purchase <i>Learn Italian - Word Power 101</i> today to start mastering Italian vocabulary in the fastest, easiest and most fun way possible! </p>"; 
